Select any a element and find all div ancestors
$x("//a[last()]/ancestor::div")

Select class attribute of body element
$x("//body/attribute::class")

Select all script descendant of head element
$x("//head/descendant::script")

Select first div child of body element, and select following-sibling
$x("//body/div[1]/following-sibling::div")

Select second div child of body element, and select preceding-sibling
$x("//body/div[2]/preceding-sibling::div")